109
00:09:11,202 --> 00:09:13,512
Saya memesan vila pribadi untuk kita di Sokcho.

110
00:09:13,512 --> 00:09:16,536
Mari kita santai saja, nikmati lautan,

111
00:09:16,536 --> 00:09:18,285
Hirup udara segar.

112
00:09:19,282 --> 00:09:21,863
